OL,3,CWhat does Grenfell tell us about the
OL,4,CBritish malaise?
OL,6,FWhy does it take so long for justice
OL,7,Fto be done when companies and
OL,8,Findividuals seemingly engage in
OL,9,Fgrotesque negligence and deception?
OL,11,FAnd why are intelligent leaders so
OL,12,Fuseless at assessing risk and reward?
OL,14,FAll of these questions flow from the
OL,15,Fdevastating report into the lethal
OL,16,Ffire in 2017 at Grenfell Tower.
