OL,3,CWhat does Grenfell tell us about the
OL,4,CBritish malaise?
OL,6,FBut many of them are also raised by
OL,7,Fthe long wait for the truth to be told
OL,8,Fabout the Hillsborough disaster, and
OL,9,Fthe even longer-running scandal of
OL,10,Flives ruined by transfusions of
OL,11,Finfected blood, and the way that Post
OL,12,FOffice executives had more confidence
OL,13,Fin a flawed IT system than in the
OL,14,Fprobity of sub-postmasters, and indeed
OL,15,Fby the hapless preparations by NHS and
OL,16,Fthe public sector more widely as Covid
OL,17,Fsurged towards these shores.
OL,19,FI could go on and on.
