OL,3,CWhat does Grenfell tell us about the
OL,4,CBritish malaise?
OL,6,FAs a nation, we've historically prided
OL,7,Fourselves on the honesty, integrity
OL,8,Fand competence of the institutions
OL,9,Fthat underpin the state and our way of
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,FBut Grenfell and the other debacles
OL,13,Fcan no longer be dismissed as
OL,14,Fexceptions to an otherwise blameless
OL,15,Fculture. Something has gone badly awry
OL,16,Fin this place.
OL,18,FIn the case of Grenfell, the summary
OL,19,Fof defects includes:
