OL,3,CWhat does Grenfell tell us about the
OL,4,CBritish malaise?
OL,6,FThe rot had already set in before
OL,7,FDavid Cameron became prime minister in
OL,8,F2010.
OL,10,FHowever, it got significantly worse
OL,11,Fwhen he started governing in coalition
OL,12,Fwith the Lib Dems, and after that, he
OL,13,Fsubsequently won the election in 2015.
