OL,3,CWhat does Grenfell tell us about the
OL,4,CBritish malaise?
OL,6,FAnd what's especially troubling is
OL,7,Fthat the decay extended as much to the
OL,8,Funelected servants of the state and to
OL,9,Fprivate sector bosses.
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer said today he wants
OL,12,Fhis government to be judged by how he
OL,13,Fresponds to the Grenfell report,
OL,14,Fwhether he reforms the culture of
OL,15,Frelevant regulation and governance and
OL,16,Falso makes safe the many thousands of
OL,17,Fbuildings still deemed at risk.
