OL,3,CWhat does Grenfell tell us about the
OL,4,CBritish malaise?
OL,6,FWhat is unclear is whether he accepts
OL,7,Fthat the tragedy at Grenfell is
OL,8,Fsymptomatic of a malaise that goes
OL,9,Fwell beyond the appalling state of
OL,10,FBritish social housing.
OL,12,FIf he does then he will know that
OL,13,Frehabilitation will be slow, painful
OL,14,Fand very expensive.
